{"tid":739643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"捱眼瞓撐英格蘭 死忠粉絲： 我哋半個國家隊嚟㗎！","createTime":"2018-07-12T09:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T15:09:26.000Z","uid":18908,"like":155,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"565346d817762cadd7542aecf4b54b12905228ed","tid":739643,"uid":18908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"觀塘商場APM昨晚再有大電視免費轉播4強準決賽，由不少港人心中愛隊英格蘭上陣大戰克羅地亞，由於今日仍是上班日，凌晨球迷人數明顯不及上周六般人頭湧湧，但直望大電視的座位仍座無虛席，部份球迷則靠在欄邊或席地而坐觀看賽事，人數一度多達近300人。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭粉絲梁先生與太太一同前來支持英格蘭，<span style=\"color: red;\"> 直言「英格蘭係我哋半個國家隊嚟㗎」</span>，因今日與太太均休假，故可以「放盡啲」看球場。他稱剛開始都怕比賽有悶場，但看了5分鐘英格蘭就有進帳，其後比賽節奏亦十分緊湊。現場所見每當英格蘭隊再現攻勢，觀眾即肉緊尖叫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/worldcup2018/news/articles/1_58431907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fworldcup2018%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F1_58431907&d=AJ%2FlWna8QFqcsDHDp9VPOZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6561765e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fworldcup2018%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F1_58431907&h=9af07ce0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/worldcup2018/news/articles/1_58431907</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好咁撚厚面皮啊香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebb91ea038561a5d08973c80264aea5ea7023b6","tid":739643,"uid":55628,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"有香港隊㗎DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d3d5d81d28d182fc831cd42874ac4bb05e65ed","tid":739643,"uid":4917,"like":19,"dislike":95,"score":-76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"第一，英格蘭唔係國家<br />\n<br />\n第二，戇鳩英撚"},{"pid":"da71e426e11327febc31aa8ec060c698a1255bfb","tid":739643,"uid":32486,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"有冇常識"},{"pid":"50874d20848463ea6844fdc675daba63fb1aaa0e","tid":739643,"uid":